Versions

Pike X.Y[{a|b}Z][plW]

X=Major number
Y=Minor number
Z=alpha/beta number
W=patch level

Examples:
The first 0.5 beta:
  Pike 0.5b1

A bug is found and corrected:
  Pike 0.5b1pl1

Pike 0.5 is here! It's a very stable version without bugs...
  Pike 0.5

An other bug is corrected (shit happens):
  Pike 0.5pl1

The next version of Pike is released as an alpha:
  Pike 0.6a1
